children.text: Located in Gravity Haus, enjoy a vibrant atmosphere at our eatery and bar, to fuel your excitement for whatever the day or night offers.

Featuring Breck's largest on-mountain patio, TenMile Station is a family-friendly quick service restaurant atop the Quicksilver Superchair on Peak 9. Check out the outdoor BBQ Depot for our signature brisket sandwich or the brisket loaded baked potato!

Enjoy beautiful views and one of the most unique dining experiences at Breck atop Peak 9. The Overlook is a quick service restaurant and bar featuring Asian inspired cuisine. Featuring our signature Mountain-Top Ramen!

Breck's newest, on-mountain quick service restaurant and full bar. Pioneer Crossing features south-of-the-border cuisine, craft beers & cocktails. Signature items include plantain rice bowls, pork green chili tacos and our cinnamon churros!

Vista Haus features beautiful panoramic views of the Great Divide, the perfect place to warm up and enjoy a meal. A quick service restaurant offering signature hand-helds such as cheesesteaks, gyros and Coney dogs!

Ski Hill Grill is Breck's flagship, quick service restaurant located at the base of Peak 8. Enjoy mountain classics from our Foodcourt, Coffee Bar, and Outdoor BBQ. Featured items include breakfast burritos, chili, pizza and burgers.
Named one of the best aprs-ski bars in North America, T-Bar is Breck's legendary aprs hot spot at the base of Peak 8! The lively slopeside bar offers craft beers, cocktails, and sharable appetizers.

data.title: Sevens
data.subtitle: At the base of Peak 7 with a sprawling deck and mountain views.

children.text: At the base of Peak 7 with a sprawling deck and mountain views. A family-friendly dining experience for breakfast, lunch, aprs or dinner.
Located in Gravity Haus, Unravel Coffee practices sustainable, collaborative coffee brewing. Grab a cup of coffee in Breckenridge with healthy food.

data.title: The Maggie
data.subtitle: Located at the base of Peak 9

children.text: Ski down, bottoms up! The Maggie is a quick service restaurant and full-bar conveniently located at the base of Peak 9, walking distance to Main Street. Featuring signature burgers and sandwiches and more than ten beers on tap!

The Living Room Restaurant and Bar offers a casual and inviting Breckenridge dining experience. Serving breakfast, lunch and Apres, The Living Room invites guests to savor Colorado inspired flavors while enjoying fresh, sustainable food.
Located inside The Maggie Restaurant serving waffles all day long.
Cluck'n-Fast Chicken! The Coop is a Grab N' Go window offering signature chicken sandwiches at the base of Peak 7.
